Author: PizzaCutter
Text: Yes, at my last psych apt he said he was going to refer me to a specialist program with CBT therapists and dieticians. My next apt isn’t until the 15th so I’m  can’t gain any weight and should probably loose a little more so that you are actually sick enough to deserve treatment. Otherwise your just faking it and don’t wasting their time, taking it away from someone who actually needs it and is really sick.

Author: HannahAching
Text: There's impostor syndrome - feeling you're not good at your job and someone will find out - and then there's us, who have impostor syndrome on having an ED. Thinking we're not really having an ED, and someone will find out. Ugh.
